      "data": {
        "title": "Start A Tiny Graph",
        "body": "Now you can ask for a graph about whatever.  The chatbot will produce a graph, and then you can talk about it or ask for changes.  You can copy and paste nodes back and forth, ask for new edges, change colors, whatever you like, until it's right.  Iterative improvement is the name of the game.",
